(3, 'How To Create a New User MySQL', '<h3 id=\"introduction\"><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-new-user-and-grant-permissions-in-mysql#introduction\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.href);\">Introduction</a><a class=\"hash-anchor\" href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-new-user-and-grant-permissions-in-mysql#introduction\" aria-hidden=\"true\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.href);\"></a></h3>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/what-is-mysql\">MySQL</a> is an open-source relational database management system. It is commonly deployed as part of the <em>LAMP stack</em> (which stands for <strong>L</strong>inux, <strong>A</strong>pache, <strong>M</strong>ySQL, and <strong>P</strong>HP) and, as of this writing, is the <a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/809750/worldwide-popularity-ranking-database-management-systems/\" rel=\"ugc nofollow\">most popular open-source database</a> in the world.</p>\r\n<p>This guide outlines how to create a new MySQL user and grant them the permissions needed to perform a variety of actions.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\"><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-new-user-and-grant-permissions-in-mysql#prerequisites\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.href);\">Prerequisites</a><a class=\"hash-anchor\" href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-new-user-and-grant-permissions-in-mysql#prerequisites\" aria-hidden=\"true\" onclick=\"navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.href);\"></a></h2>\r\n<p>In order to follow along with this guide, you&rsquo;ll need access to a MySQL database. This guide assumes that this database is installed on a virtual private server running Ubuntu 20.04, though the principles it outlines should be applicable regardless of how you access your database.</p>\r\n<p>If you don&rsquo;t have access to a MySQL database and would like to set one up yourself, you can follow one of our guides on <a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorial-collections/how-to-install-mysql\">How To Install MySQL</a>. Again, regardless of your server&rsquo;s underlying operating system, the methods for creating a new MySQL user and granting them permissions will generally be the same.</p>', 1, '665f8ab003019.png', '2024-02-14 22:28:05'),
(9, 'Tutorial PHP', '<h1 class=\"blue\">Tutorial PHP : comment apprendre PHP pour d&eacute;butants</h1>\r\n<p>PHP est l&rsquo;un des langages de programmation les plus courants pour la <strong>programmation c&ocirc;t&eacute; serveur</strong>. Au fil du temps, PHP est devenu un &eacute;l&eacute;ment indispensable de nombreux sites Web et technologies Internet modernes. Apprendre PHP peut toutefois &ecirc;tre un d&eacute;fi consid&eacute;rable pour les d&eacute;butants. Dans ce tutoriel PHP, nous vous pr&eacute;sentons les bases de ce langage de programmation appr&eacute;ci&eacute;, ainsi que les principaux op&eacute;rateurs, boucles et fonctions.</p>\r\n<div class=\"tx-toc\">\r\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc content-table smoothscroll numbers togglestyle\">\r\n<div id=\"toctitle\" class=\"opener\"><strong class=\"h3\">Sommaire</strong><span class=\"toctoggle\"><a href=\"https://www.ionos.fr/digitalguide/sites-internet/creation-de-sites-internet/apprendre-php/\" id=\"togglelinkStyle\"></a></span></div>\r\n<ol class=\"ordered-list list-content toclist hierarchy\">\r\n<li class=\"toclevel-1\"><a class=\"toc-item-link\" href=\"https://www.ionos.fr/digitalguide/sites-internet/creation-de-sites-internet/apprendre-php/#content-php-tutorial--ce-que-vous-devez-prvoir\"><span class=\"toctext\" data-slug=\"content-php-tutorial--ce-que-vous-devez-prvoir\"> PHP tutorial : ce que vous devez pr&eacute;voir </span></a></li>\r\n<li class=\"toclevel-1\"><a class=\"toc-item-link\" href=\"https://www.ionos.fr/digitalguide/sites-internet/creation-de-sites-internet/apprendre-php/#content-bases-de-php--la-syntaxe-du-langage-de-script\"><span class=\"toctext\" data-slug=\"content-bases-de-php--la-syntaxe-du-langage-de-script\"> Bases de PHP : la syntaxe du langage de script </span></a></li>\r\n<li class=\"toclevel-1\"><a class=\"toc-item-link\" href=\"https://www.ionos.fr/digitalguide/sites-internet/creation-de-sites-internet/apprendre-php/#content-les-superglobals-get-et-post\"><span class=\